entities.label: Project
entities.name: The High School Coding Club in Anytown, USA
entities.summary: The High School Coding Club in Anytown, USA aims to bridge the knowledge gap by creating an interactive, web-based platform to introduce basic coding concepts to elementary school children.

entities.label: Goal
entities.name: The unique project
entities.summary: The goal of the project is to create an interactive, web-based platform that introduces basic coding concepts through gamified experiences, making technology accessible and enjoyable for young learners.

entities.label: Technology
entities.name: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js, Python, Django framework, PostgreSQL
